strings: <voice_0x01000D48><se_high>Red: Don't often see your face round these parts any more, Yangus. So...what brings you here?
<voice_0x01000D49><se_low>Yangus: It's like this, Red... You bought an 'orse from the black market drum in Pickham, right?
<voice_0x01000D4A><se_low>Yangus: Well it belongs to this bloke I'm travellin' wiv, see. Someone pinched it off 'im and then sold it on. That's 'ow it came to be in the shop.

<voice_0x01000D4B><se_low>Yangus: I ain't gonna beat around the bush.
I need it back. I'll pay wotever ya want for it.
Name yer price.

<voice_0x01000D4C><se_high>Red: Straight up as usual, eh, Yangus.
I like that about you.
<voice_0x01000D4D><se_high>Red: But I'm not sellin' that horse. She's a quality mare. Tows the line and she's got a decent coat on her.

<voice_0x01000D4E><se_high>Red: You know how much I like quality!
However much you're willin' to pay,
I am not partin' with it!

<voice_0x01000D4F><se_low>Yangus: Wot!? Not for nuffin'?
Look, it ain't for me, it's for me mate.
I've gotta get 'er back...
I'll do anyfin' you want.

<voice_0x01000D50><se_high>Red: Interestin'... Never thought I'd hear words
like that comin' out of your mouth.
Must be a good mate, eh?

<voice_0x01000D51><se_high>Red: Awright, then.
Here's what you're gonna do.
<voice_0x01000D52><se_high>Red: I'm sure you haven't forgotten the cave just north of here, right?

<voice_0x01000D53><se_high>Red: Just bring us the jewel that's hidden in there.
You know, the Venus' tear.

<voice_0x01000D54><se_low>Yangus: Wot!? Not that!
You know I been in that cave before, an'...

<voice_0x01000D55><se_high>Red: You just said you'd do anyfin' I want!
You gonna welch on that now, are ya?

<voice_0x01000D56><se_high>Red: Just bring us the Venus' tear.
Then I'll think about the 'orse.

<voice_0x01000D57><se_low>Yangus: Er...right...then...
Guess I'll be on me way then, eh.
